{"kind":"blogger#post","id":"4314568632533477382","blog":{"id":"2360593805083673688"},"published":"2010-10-08T02:00:00-07:00","updated":"2010-10-28T18:07:49-07:00","url":"http://www.quietlikehorses.com/2010/10/4-ways-to-wear-boots-this-fall.html","selfLink":"https://www.googleapis.com/blogger/v3/blogs/2360593805083673688/posts/4314568632533477382","title":"4 Ways to Wear Boots This Fall","content":"<a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_mkw1MyhyGTY/TK6dioJYq0I/AAAAAAAAEhc/kGiA0LLDxJM/s1600/frye+boots.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 600px; height: 400px;\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_mkw1MyhyGTY/TK6dioJYq0I/AAAAAAAAEhc/kGiA0LLDxJM/s1600/frye+boots.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5525527011048074050\" border=\"0\" /></a>This season, I decided to invest in a nice pair of boots. After trying on dozens of different kinds, I decided on a tall pair by Frye. I also waited to pick a pair during the Nordstrom Anniversary Sale (<span style=\"font-style: italic;\">such</span> a good time to stock up on fall essentials!) since boots can be a bit of an investment. These boots are seriously comfortable and forgiving on my wide feet, but what I love most is how versatile they are. Here are some of my favorite ideas on how to style your fall boots:<br /><br /><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_mkw1MyhyGTY/TK6diSOWbQI/AAAAAAAAEhU/AY71nlUIhgM/s1600/with+black+slim+pants.JPG\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 450px; height: 473px;\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_mkw1MyhyGTY/TK6diSOWbQI/AAAAAAAAEhU/AY71nlUIhgM/s1600/with+black+slim+pants.JPG\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5525527005163318530\" border=\"0\" /></a>1) Black and brown: Tuck skinny black pants into your boots to update a classic black and white color combo.<br /><br /><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_mkw1MyhyGTY/TK6dh4EVTUI/AAAAAAAAEhE/LTN7zmLd23E/s1600/with+longer+skirts.JPG\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 450px; height: 672px;\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_mkw1MyhyGTY/TK6dh4EVTUI/AAAAAAAAEhE/LTN7zmLd23E/s1600/with+longer+skirts.JPG\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5525526998141979970\" border=\"0\" /></a>2) Skirting the issue: No time to shave in the morning? Wear tall boots with a longer skirt. No socks, hosiery, or razors required.<br /><br /><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_mkw1MyhyGTY/TK6diB3FfoI/AAAAAAAAEhM/rA-c68ixlzQ/s1600/with+over+the+knee+socks.JPG\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 450px; height: 721px;\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_mkw1MyhyGTY/TK6diB3FfoI/AAAAAAAAEhM/rA-c68ixlzQ/s1600/with+over+the+knee+socks.JPG\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5525527000770772610\" border=\"0\" /></a>3) Over-the-top: I've been wanting to try over-the-knee socks for a while. The verdict? They're thick, warm, and make short skirts fall-appropriate.<br /><br /><a onblur=\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_mkw1MyhyGTY/TK6dhmVwaMI/AAAAAAAAEg8/Gyjh6b4Ny-U/s1600/cuffed+boots+with+tights.jpg\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 450px; height: 672px;\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_mkw1MyhyGTY/TK6dhmVwaMI/AAAAAAAAEg8/Gyjh6b4Ny-U/s1600/cuffed+boots+with+tights.jpg\" alt=\"\" id=\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5525526993383221442\" border=\"0\" /></a>4) Cuffs &amp; tights: For those days when you're feelin' extra sassy, pull on a pair of textured tights, fold your boots over and get ready to shake your booties.<br /><br />(You can see the other pictures my friend Thai took <a href=\"http://bit.ly/9gzl6u\">right here</a>.)","author":{"id":"06629562195146939698","displayName":"Sobrina Tung","url":"http://www.blogger.com/profile/06629562195146939698","image":{"url":"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_mkw1MyhyGTY/TI8X4CO5nWI/AAAAAAAAERk/4p5D74gYdFE/S45/me.JPG"}},"replies":{"totalItems":"14","selfLink":"https://www.googleapis.com/blogger/v3/blogs/2360593805083673688/posts/4314568632533477382/comments"}}